56" class="r-1n5p5n"><div data-rid="06536144-ba60-48b8-932b-86a58d5b5acb" class="r-nlm178 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85)">YES!!! Even if you have had sensitivity in the past, you may not have any with POOOF!®. We have designed POOOF!® with a proprietary P3 additive plus Hydroxyapatite for our low to no sensitivity solution. If you do, it is important to know that any tooth sensitivity as a result of whitening is always transitory and will always dissipate.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="15cc278a-9d89-4336-aa42-6366a4ab6bc9" class="r-xsme7a" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="2418f7ed-ec92-457c-8b1d-e39eda31e671" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R2r32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-12pg921"><div data-rid="31f291fd-34c6-4930-a879-c52343201b6e" class="r-1hiqtjm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h5><strong>How long will it take to see results with whitening strips?</strong></h5></span></div><div data-rid="ebdab3f6-5d49-46af-ac72-2c3d614f7dc4" class="r-i8r6oa" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1por5ro" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2r32:"><div data-rid="308ae2c7-969a-4cfc-8819-813a4cbff3a3" class="r-1oy006w"><div data-rid="781da119-7aed-4100-ab97-7cb11991ce25" class="r-zqyecn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85)">Results are often seen immediately after the first use! However, in an independent clinical study, after a 10-day in-vitro utilization, POOOF!® Whitening Strips showed 37% </span><strong>BETTER</strong><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85)"> whitening than the leading whitening strips.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="2edabe5a-0467-4651-9b18-3167bd39a2b5" class="r-10b51l6" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="507cd192-320a-4149-b07d-af5e416ba13b" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3b32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1htkbzv"><div data-rid="43efb696-1830-4ff2-9151-382cc9554c3a" class="r-d4e2vn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h5><strong>How do I store whitening strips properly?</strong></h5></span></div><div data-rid="9ece7a5b-9c7c-4ba1-ab0a-dcdd06490ae6" class="r-543wfa" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:100%" class="r-1bgczty" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R3b32:"><div data-rid="f9b623e3-2cf3-4dc4-8da9-053a58d208b5" class="r-rw6968"><div data-rid="c757d239-7c51-43db-95b5-93619e9acd81" class="r-auhque alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(85, 85, 85)">It is best to store strips at room temperature. If you live in a warm climate you may keep the strips In a cool dry place, however under normal circumstances, this is not required.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="1e53feb5-5033-4410-8d9e-6220fa486551" class="r-rcz30" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="6f153a8f-8a93-476f-88c6-9c2d89d6fbee" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3r32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1syjpc2"><div data-rid="490ef6a1-4fdf-470c-8b20-577dd0fd605f" class="r-142ryfu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h5><strong>Are whitening strips suitable for everyone?</strong></